---
layout: base.njk
title: "Blog — Engineering Insights | Surya Prakash Reddy"
description: "Thoughts on Java, microservices, cloud architecture, and engineering leadership from 8+ years in financial services."
permalink: /blog/
---

<div class="blog-listing-page">
  <div class="blog-listing-hero">
    <div class="section-label">Writing</div>
    <h1 class="section-title">The Blog</h1>
    <p class="blog-listing-sub">
      Thoughts on Java, microservices, AWS, and building software in financial services.<br>
      Lessons from 8+ years shipping production code at Lloyd's of London and beyond.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="blog-listing-grid">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="blog-card reveal">
      <div class="blog-card-meta">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <span class="blog-card-reading">{{ post.content | readingTime }}</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="blog-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      {% if post.data.description %}
        <p class="blog-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if post.data.tags %}
        <div class="blog-card-tags">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
            {% if tag != "blog" %}
              <span class="blog-card-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      <span class="blog-card-cta">Read article →</span>
    </a>
    {% else %}
    <p class="blog-empty">No posts yet — check back soon.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
